        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[This release adds support for the Java 21 preview feature: unnamed patterns and variables (JEP 443)!]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>This release adds support for the Java 21 preview feature: unnamed patterns and variables (<a href="https://openjdk.org/jeps/443" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">JEP 443</a>)!</p>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="highlights">Highlights<a href="https://jtkiesel.github.io/prettier-java/blog/2023/11/26/2.5.0#highlights" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Highlights" title="Direct link to Highlights">​</a></h2>
<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="support-java-21-preview-feature-unnamed-patterns-and-variables-620-by-jtkiesel">Support Java 21 preview feature: unnamed patterns and variables (<a href="https://github.com/jhipster/prettier-java/pull/620" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">#620</a> by <a href="https://github.com/jtkiesel" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">@jtkiesel</a>)<a href="https://jtkiesel.github.io/prettier-java/blog/2023/11/26/2.5.0#support-java-21-preview-feature-unnamed-patterns-and-variables-620-by-jtkiesel" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to support-java-21-preview-feature-unnamed-patterns-and-variables-620-by-jtkiesel" title="Direct link to support-java-21-preview-feature-unnamed-patterns-and-variables-620-by-jtkiesel">​</a></h3>
<p>We’ve added support for the Java 21 preview feature "Unnamed Patterns and Variables":</p>
<h4 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="unnamed-pattern-variables">Unnamed pattern variables<a href="https://jtkiesel.github.io/prettier-java/blog/2023/11/26/2.5.0#unnamed-pattern-variables" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Unnamed pattern variables" title="Direct link to Unnamed pattern variables">​</a></h4>
<div class="language-java codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-java codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">// Examples</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">r instanceof Point _</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_y97N"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>
<h4 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="unnamed-variables">Unnamed variables<a href="https://jtkiesel.github.io/prettier-java/blog/2023/11/26/2.5.0#unnamed-variables" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Unnamed variables" title="Direct link to Unnamed variables">​</a></h4>
<div class="language-java codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-java codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">// Example</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">int acc = 0;</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">for (Order _ : orders) {</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  if (acc &lt; LIMIT) {</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">    // ... acc++ ...</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  }</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">}</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_y97N"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="other-changes">Other Changes<a href="https://jtkiesel.github.io/prettier-java/blog/2023/11/26/2.5.0#other-changes" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Other Changes" title="Direct link to Other Changes">​</a></h2>
<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="new-entrypoint-lexandparse-to-return-both-tokens-and-cst-625-by-max-schaefer">New entrypoint <code>lexAndParse</code> to return both tokens and CST (<a href="https://github.com/jhipster/prettier-java/pull/625" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">#625</a> by <a href="https://github.com/max-schaefer" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">@max-schaefer</a>)<a href="https://jtkiesel.github.io/prettier-java/blog/2023/11/26/2.5.0#new-entrypoint-lexandparse-to-return-both-tokens-and-cst-625-by-max-schaefer" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to new-entrypoint-lexandparse-to-return-both-tokens-and-cst-625-by-max-schaefer" title="Direct link to new-entrypoint-lexandparse-to-return-both-tokens-and-cst-625-by-max-schaefer">​</a></h3>
<p>Provide an entrypoint that exposes both the CST and the underlying token array.</p>
<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="no-longer-ignore-whole-block-when-prettier-ignore-at-start-603-by-jtkiesel">No longer ignore whole block when <code>prettier-ignore</code> at start (<a href="https://github.com/jhipster/prettier-java/pull/603" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">#603</a> by <a href="https://github.com/jtkiesel" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">@jtkiesel</a>)<a href="https://jtkiesel.github.io/prettier-java/blog/2023/11/26/2.5.0#no-longer-ignore-whole-block-when-prettier-ignore-at-start-603-by-jtkiesel" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to no-longer-ignore-whole-block-when-prettier-ignore-at-start-603-by-jtkiesel" title="Direct link to no-longer-ignore-whole-block-when-prettier-ignore-at-start-603-by-jtkiesel">​</a></h3>
<p>When a block begins with <code>// prettier-ignore</code>, only the first statement is ignored, rather than the whole block.</p>
<div class="language-java codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-java codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">// Input</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">void foo() {</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  // prettier-ignore</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  var bar = List.of(</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">    1</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  );</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">    var baz = 2;</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">}</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">// Prettier Java 2.4</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">void foo() {</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  // prettier-ignore</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  var bar = List.of(</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">    1</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  );</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">    var baz = 2;</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">}</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">// Prettier Java 2.5</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">void foo() {</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  // prettier-ignore</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  var bar = List.of(</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">    1</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  );</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  var baz = 2;</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">}</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_y97N"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>]]></conte